Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maminko! Maminko! Maminko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo?
